				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I like this spell, it can hold a mob at tops for a good 2 minutes. At worst it can break in 15 seconds. Like everything else in EQ how effective this spell is against the mob dpends on the comparision in levels of you and that mob. If you're casting this on white and yellow cons (though you'll be daft to if you are soloing at this level 49+) you can do nothing but expect it to be broken and resisted a lot. EQ is about finding the right tactic against mobs solo and in groups (yes we druids do group sometimes). Some blue cons especially named mobs will resist the root a lot unless you're a good ten or so levels above it. If you speciliased in conjure and have all your dots (upto lvl 53) stack all your three dots (roughly 3K dmg) and watch that mob health bar drop and it does drop fast.<BR>
<BR>
Only tried this spell in Cobalt Scar, Burning wood and Skyfire, it works well here for me. Have not tried it in a dungeon.
